transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Ah ji sir very good morning. Ashok ji baat kar rahe hain sir Jai Mahakal Traders mein?
Customer: Haan baat kar raha hoon.
Executive: Ashok ji main Vidhi baat kar rahi thi India Mart team se. Kaise hain aap?
Customer: Haan badhiya hai.
Executive: Actually aapka ek feedback receive hua tha sir aapki services ke regarding aap satisfied nahi ho right?
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Kya problem aa rahi thi sir?
Customer: Kuch bhi nahi.
Executive: Ah but sir aapne to not satisfied mark kiya hua hai. Kal shayad aapke Bharat se baat hui thi aapke jo account manager hai right?
Customer: Hmm.
Executive: Unke discussion ke baad aapne unko not satisfied kiya to matlab like unhone aapki problem solve nahi ki sir ya kya reason tha?
Customer: Koi problem hi nahi hai na. Main to usme kuch problem to nahi hai. Wo aane ke liye bol rahe the maine mana kar diya khatam.
Executive: Okay. So fir sir not satisfied kyun kiya aapne? Matlab koi to problem hogi na sir tabhi to aapne no diya hai na?
Customer: Nahi maine nahi kiya.
